---
title: Welsh Rarebit Veggie Shepherd's Pie with Lentils and Mushrooms
description: Our Welsh Rarebit Veggie Shepherd's Pie is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/welsh-rarebit-veggie-shepherd-s-pie-ba026dd4-720cea9a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/welsh-rarebit-veggie-shepherd-s-pie-623709768a63544ace5e3e66-eaa5d290.pdf
